<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>You Have a New IWF Challenge!</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="color: #a00;">You Have Been Challenged!</h1>
    <p>Hello {{ defender_name }},</p>
    <p>
        <strong>{{ challenger_name }}</strong> has challenged you to a match in the Internet Wrestling Federation!
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>Wager Amount:</strong> {{ wager_amount }} Gold
    </p>
    <p>
